title: Creative Vegetarian
description: Chinese name 创意素食. A 2-floor Chinese vegan food restaurant, opened in September 2011. Also delivers food for lunch and dinner. Located in north Kunming in the Panlong District. Nice design with light colors and comfortable tables. Address in Chinese: 盘龙区环城东路上东城一期1-9商铺(近东华手机大厦).
streetAddress: 1-9 Shangdongcheng, Huancheng East Rd., Panlong District
